Physics is a natural science that deals with the study of matter and energy in the universe, including their behavior and interactions. The size of blank pages in Publisher consisting of 4 bond papers would depend on the size of each bond paper. Bond paper sizes can vary depending on the country/region of origin, and there are also different standards for paper sizes (e.g. US standard vs ISO standard). 

Assuming the bond paper size is 8.5 inches by 11 inches (which is the standard size for US letter paper), the size of four bond papers laid out side by side would measure approximately 17 inches by 22 inches. This means that the size of the blank pages in Publisher consisting of 4 bond papers would also be 17 inches by 22 inches.
